Alembic migrations for LlamaBot auth database.

This directory contains database migrations managed by Alembic.
Migrations are run automatically on application startup.

Commands (from the app/ directory):

  # Generate a new migration after changing models.py
  alembic revision --autogenerate -m "description of change"

  # Run all pending migrations manually
  alembic upgrade head

  # Downgrade to previous version
  alembic downgrade -1

  # Show current revision
  alembic current

  # Show migration history
  alembic history
